title: Duncan Ende (Racing driver)
description: Pro driver Duncan Ende joins us to talk about ALMS, racetracks, the intricacies of supercars, racing strategy, R8 race cars vs R8 street cars, and we answer listener questions.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
